sentences: She became famous under the stage name I BEE in the 1990s during the period of popularity of dance music in Croatia.
She released her first album in 1991.
She also took part in a hugely successful duet with Bosnian vocalist Dino Merlin called "Godinama" in 2000, a song which achieved popularity throughout the former Yugoslavia.
The song won a Porin Award for Hit of the Year in 2001.
